data.description: Discover your ideal home in the coveted Kernan Boulevard area! This charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence spans 1,501 square feet, offering both comfort and convenience. Located just a quick 10-minute drive from the beach, you'll enjoy easy access to shopping, gyms, and more nearby. Plus, grocery stores are within biking distance for added convenience.  This home presents an excellent opportunity in a prime location. All appliances are new and will convey with the property, ensuring a seamless move-in experience. With a roof and HVAC system less than 10 years old, you'll have peace of mind knowing your home is well-maintained. Don't miss out on this chance to embrace the perfect blend of location and quality living!
